<h1 metal:fill-slot="content-header" 
    i18n:translate="">About SchoolTool</h1>

<div metal:fill-slot="body">

<p i18n:translate="">SchoolTool is free administrative software for schools 
around the world.  The goals of the project are to create a simple 
turnkey student information system or managment information system for primary 
and secondary schools, as well as a framework for building customized 
applications and configurations for individual schools or states.</p>

<p i18n:translate="">SchoolTool is built on a 100% open source software stack,
written in <a href="http://python.org">Python</a> using the 
<a href="http://zope.org">Zope 3</a> framework.</p>

<p i18n:translate="">SchoolTool is licensed under the 
<a href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html">GNU General Public 
License, Version 2</a>.</p>

