<ul>
<li><a href="http://schooltool.org" i18n:translate="">Website</a></li>
<li><a href="https://launchpad.net/schooltool-project" i18n:translate="">Launchpad project page</a></li>
<li><a href="https://launchpad.net/~schooltoolers" i18n:translate="">Mailing list</a></li>
